00:07:06.680 --> 00:07:08.190
Who cut one person out?

00:07:08.510 --> 00:07:09.860
It should be three people, right?

00:07:11.510 --> 00:07:13.170
Since it was cut,
why still keep it there?

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:15.510
We have always been friends.

00:07:17.600 --> 00:07:19.510
You don't want to be the one

00:07:19.510 --> 00:07:21.190
who sends Zhang Yutong to prison,

00:07:22.070 --> 00:07:25.240
because you feel you owe her.

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:28.270
You disposed of the body for her.

00:07:32.680 --> 00:07:34.510
You thought Chen might end up in prison

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:37.510
because of Zhang's crime,

00:07:38.070 --> 00:07:40.160
and you felt sorry for Chen,

00:07:42.190 --> 00:07:43.030
