00:09:53.390 --> 00:09:54.230
What medicine?

00:09:55.150 --> 00:09:57.000
I haven't seen Zhang Yutong

00:09:57.790 --> 00:09:58.910
for about five or six years.

00:10:00.840 --> 00:10:01.840
Let me help you recall.

00:10:14.440 --> 00:10:15.550
You found an excuse

00:10:15.750 --> 00:10:17.200
to have Wang Chen invite her out.

00:10:17.750 --> 00:10:19.600
You deliberately spilled water on her.

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:21.630
When she was tidying up,

00:10:22.360 --> 00:10:23.460
you switched her medicine.

00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:31.960
I can arrange

00:10:32.440 --> 00:10:34.080
videos like this

00:10:34.080 --> 00:10:35.440
into 100 different stories.

00:10:36.790 --> 00:10:38.910
Storytelling is your profession.

00:10:39.270 --> 00:10:40.510
Ensuring the people's safety

00:10:40.510 --> 00:10:41.440
is my occupation.

00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:43.360
We've got the medicine.

00:10:46.740 --> 00:10:47.840
The capsule shell is real.

00:10:47.840 --> 00:10:49.180
The substance inside is Buspirone.

00:10:49.180 --> 00:10:50.820
